=ML-07 Polynomial Evaluation=

Consider a polynomial:
:''P(x) = a0 + a1.x + ... + an.x^n''

To evaluate ''P(x)'':
# ''n'' $$A$$
# $$0 B$$ (This means that we will start with a0)
# $$a0 R/S a1 R/S ... an R/S$$
# $$C$$

==Example==

Compute ''P(x) = 3 - 2x + x^4'' at ''x = 2'':
* $$4 A$$
* $$0 B 3 R/S 2 +/- R/S 0 R/S 0 R/S 1 R/S$$
* $$C$$: @@15@@
